December 1994    2.9       2.8       5.8       2.1     95.9
January 1995     3.3       3.5       4.6       2.2     95.9

February         3.4       3.6       5.6       2.5     94.4
March            3.5       3.8       4.8       1.2     92.5
April            3.3       4.2       5.2       2.8     91.2
May              3.4       4.2       4.5       3.4     91.0
