Sazerac to Rep Chateau Roubine


     Chateau Roubine named Sazerac Co. its exclusive distributor,
succeeding Carillon Importers.
     Peter Bordeaux, Sazerac president, said Chateau Roubine is
among the Cote de Provence vineyards producing wine under the AOC
status.  Production consists of 60% rose, 30% and 10% white and is
largely in the Cru Class.




