     Evian Natural Spring Water is running a fitness-themed

     Evian Natural Spring Water is running a fitness-themed
cross-promotion this month with the Neiman Marcus department store
chain. Neiman Marcus shoppers who spend $50 or more will receive as
a free gift a 1-liter bottle of Evian, a Neiman Marcus backpack and the
new exercise video Perfectly Fit, which features supermodel Claudia
Schiffer. In addition, all the Neiman Marcus stores nationwide will serve
only Evian in their restaurants, and Evian kiosks will be located
throughout each store. The promotion is supported by in-store window
displays and signage, newspaper and radio ads, and direct mail pieces
sent to 750,000 Neiman Marcus customers.




