QUALITY:     High fertility.
PACKAGE:     Jarswith liquid nitrogen.
DELIVERY:    immediate.
OTHER:       Firstpurchase in the U.S
QUOTE:       According to place.
BANK REF:    National Bank of Internal Trade, Acambaro Guanajuato.
CONTACT:     MVZ Fernando L.pez, Veterinaria "El Rancho", J. Aldama
             39-B,Acambaro, Guanajuato, 38600 Mexico
PHONE:       (011-52-417) 2-5476
FAX:         (011-52-417) 2-3107.

