PIER 1'S $20 MILLION QUESTION

By:
EDITED BY THANE PETERSON

PIER 1 IMPORTS ALSO HAD A lump of coal in its Christmas stocking: The
retailer disclosed on Dec. 26 that it would post a pretax loss of $20
